@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state Power-On_Check
state Startup_Problem
state Ready
state Monitoring
state Alarm_Triggered
state Normal

Power-On_Check --> Startup_Problem : [Problem detected]
Power-On_Check --> Ready : [Everything fine]

Ready --> Ready : [User resets]
Ready --> Monitoring : [User activates]
Ready --> Normal : [User turns off]

Monitoring --> Alarm_Triggered : [Sensor triggered]
Monitoring --> Monitoring : [False alarm or time ends]
Monitoring --> Normal : [User enters password]

Alarm_Triggered --> Normal : [User enters password]

@enduml
